Nightsong is pulled from the ritual with an uncomfortable realization

synopsis.value: Players encounter Nightsong in the depths of Shar's Labyrinth. She summons Shades with a song that they must defeat, then tells them she was cursed by Ketheric to be in this form. Players can either promise to free Nightsong, leave her to the curse, or kill her.
